1
00:00:15,300 --> 00:00:19,400
♫ The top of the mountains where the snow never melts ♫

2
00:00:19,400 --> 00:00:22,800
♫ The plains where the wind blows ♫

3
00:00:22,800 --> 00:00:30,700
♫ What finds me in my sleep are the nightmares about you ♫

4
00:00:30,700 --> 00:00:34,600
♫ In the endless abyss ♫

5
00:00:34,600 --> 00:00:38,000
♫ Your face gradually emerges ♫

6
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:46,000
♫ A love that budded unknowingly to us continues
to grow and blossom ♫

7
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:53,400
♫ Who risked his life for mine? ♫

8
00:00:53,400 --> 00:01:00,100
♫ I had braced myself for the end, but my heart frets for you ♫

9
00:01:00,100 --> 00:01:07,800
♫ It turns out there is an end to my waiting for you ♫

10
00:01:07,800 --> 00:01:16,200
♫ At the hills where the grasslands end where
it will always be spring ♫

11
00:01:16,200 --> 00:01:23,600
♫ I find the boundless river of stars in your eyes ♫

12
00:01:25,800 --> 00:01:33,000
♫ Only with your hand in mine is this life worthwhile ♫

13
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:37,300
[Shining Just for You]

14
00:01:37,300 --> 00:01:39,900
[Episode 13]

15
00:01:40,800 --> 00:01:42,800
It has left, right?

16
00:01:42,800 --> 00:01:44,800
Are you crazy?

17
00:01:44,800 --> 00:01:46,800
Do you know what you were doing?

18
00:01:46,800 --> 00:01:49,200
I was looking for a Truth Master?

19
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:51,200
Truth Master?

20
00:01:51,200 --> 00:01:54,500
If it promises you a gift, will you take it?

21
00:01:54,500 --> 00:01:58,200
Risking your own life for a nonsensical matter like this,

22
00:01:58,200 --> 00:02:00,000
are you an idiot?

23
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:02,600
Your Majesty! Your Majesty!

24
00:02:02,600 --> 00:02:04,200
Your Majesty!

25
00:02:18,600 --> 00:02:21,600
What are you staring at? Are you blind?

26
00:02:22,400 --> 00:02:24,000
Summon the imperial physician.

27
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:25,800
Tell him to give her a diagnosis.

28
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:27,500
Yes, Your Majesty.

29
00:02:28,900 --> 00:02:31,500
If so, will you still look for the Truth...

30
00:02:31,500 --> 00:02:32,800
Official Bai.

31
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:35,400
Please.

32
00:03:02,500 --> 00:03:04,800
Why did you only come back now?

33
00:03:07,300 --> 00:03:11,000
You knew that the Truth Master wasn't under Mianshi Bridge, right?

34
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:13,000
The python you saw is called Feiguang.

35
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:15,600
It's not the Truth Master.

36
00:03:15,600 --> 00:03:18,200
However, it's guarding a magic array that's vital to the Truth Master.

37
00:03:18,200 --> 00:03:21,500
Moreover, you came back alive, didn't you?

38
00:03:24,300 --> 00:03:26,000
He saved me.

39
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:28,200
I expected that to happen.

40
00:03:28,200 --> 00:03:30,400
Your celestial power was sealed away long ago.

41
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:33,000
You can never escape from it.

42
00:03:35,100 --> 00:03:38,000
Yu Xiuming has exposed my lie.

43
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:41,500
I don't even know what a Truth Master is.

44
00:03:41,500 --> 00:03:43,700
What should I do now?

45
00:03:43,700 --> 00:03:47,400
I think Yu Xiuming won't take your life.

46
00:03:47,400 --> 00:03:49,600
His birthday is on the Emperor's Natal Day.

47
00:03:49,600 --> 00:03:50,900
You should try to coax him.

48
00:03:50,900 --> 00:03:53,200
Maybe he'll let you off.

49
00:04:03,600 --> 00:04:07,400
[Jianyue Pavilion]

50
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:23,400
- Wait here.
- Yes, sir.

51
00:04:23,400 --> 00:04:25,900
[Xue Xuanjing, Protectorate General of Ningzhou]

52
00:04:40,700 --> 00:04:43,200
Sir, please take care. Come again.

53
00:04:43,200 --> 00:04:44,600
Sir.

54
00:04:46,200 --> 00:04:48,100
Over here, please.

55
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:02,200
Young Master, the Protectorate General of Ningzhou wishes to see you.

56
00:05:07,300 --> 00:05:08,700
Your Highness.

57
00:05:21,200 --> 00:05:23,200
It's been a long time.

58
00:05:23,200 --> 00:05:25,600
You're doing exceptionally well now.

59
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:27,700
This is an occasion worth celebrating.

60
00:05:27,700 --> 00:05:30,000
My effort wasn't in vain indeed.

61
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:33,200
Protectorate General, thank you for sparing me back then.

62
00:05:33,200 --> 00:05:35,800
That's how I was able to drag out my ignoble existence.

63
00:05:38,600 --> 00:05:41,400
Your Highness, you must be joking.

64
00:05:41,400 --> 00:05:45,300
When I was young, the Winged Emperor protected me.

65
00:05:45,300 --> 00:05:47,600
I am forever grateful to him.

66
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:50,200
Your Highness, you're the only descendant of my benefactor.

67
00:05:50,200 --> 00:05:52,200
When I heard that you were in Tianqi,

68
00:05:52,200 --> 00:05:55,300
I was truly worried about your safety.

69
00:05:57,200 --> 00:05:59,100
Protectorate General, as you can see,

70
00:05:59,100 --> 00:06:02,000
I'm doing well in Tianqi

71
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:05,400
and leading a carefree life here.

72
00:06:05,400 --> 00:06:07,000
The Yu Family is long gone.

73
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:10,100
Yu Linkong no longer exists in this world.

74
00:06:10,100 --> 00:06:12,000
I'm Yi Wuyou.

75
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:16,000
Protectorate General, please stop calling me by my old name.

76
00:06:20,200 --> 00:06:21,600
Your Highness.

77
00:06:25,200 --> 00:06:29,800
Your Highness, you might have misunderstood something.

78
00:06:29,800 --> 00:06:33,500
Back then, your father wasn't willing to form an alliance with Yu Xiuming.

79
00:06:33,500 --> 00:06:35,000
As for me,

80
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:38,700
I was hesitating about the alliance, too.

81
00:06:38,700 --> 00:06:41,400
However, Yu Xiuming was renowned for winning 100 battles.

82
00:06:41,400 --> 00:06:44,600
The Winged Clan wasn't willing to stand against him until the end.

83
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:46,200
Although your father was revered by his people,

84
00:06:46,200 --> 00:06:48,800
he couldn't convince the people to join him.

85
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:52,900
In the end, all the city lords decided to yield to the humans.

86
00:06:52,900 --> 00:06:54,600
But the traitors were the most detestable.

87
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:57,900
They ratted your father out by reporting him to Yu Xiuming, saying that he would be a nuisance to him.

88
00:06:57,900 --> 00:07:02,100
I have no intention of clarifying the rumors back then.

89
00:07:02,100 --> 00:07:04,900
Right now, I'm only a businessman.

90
00:07:04,900 --> 00:07:08,200
Ningzhou has nothing to do with me.

91
00:07:08,200 --> 00:07:11,700
Your Highness is extraordinary indeed.

92
00:07:11,700 --> 00:07:13,600
It's just that...

93
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:17,400
Protectorate General, don't tell me you came all the way here just to catch up with me?

94
00:07:17,400 --> 00:07:19,500
What exactly is your intention?

95
00:07:19,500 --> 00:07:21,400
Your Highness, to be honest,

96
00:07:22,200 --> 00:07:25,300
I would like to invite you to return to Ningzhou.

97
00:07:25,300 --> 00:07:27,700
I will aid you in rebuilding the Winged Clan

98
00:07:27,700 --> 00:07:30,000
and its prestige.

99
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:33,900
You might not know, but I get sentimental

100
00:07:33,900 --> 00:07:37,600
whenever I am reminded of your father.

101
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:40,800
I was thinking that I shoulddo something for your sake.

102
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:42,200
Protectorate General, please return.

103
00:07:42,200 --> 00:07:45,300
I won't return to Ningzhou.

104
00:07:50,300 --> 00:07:53,600
Your Highness, you don't need to reject me immediately.

105
00:07:53,600 --> 00:07:56,200
I shall excuse myself now.

106
00:07:56,200 --> 00:07:58,000
Farewell.

107
00:08:22,700 --> 00:08:23,800
Father.

108
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:47,200
You knew that he wouldn't work together with us.

109
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:49,900
Why did you make me come here personally?

110
00:08:49,900 --> 00:08:51,700
If he's someone who can be easily manipulated by others,

111
00:08:51,700 --> 00:08:55,000
I would never suggest you recruit him, Father.

112
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:56,200
What do you mean?

113
00:08:56,200 --> 00:08:59,900
Since he's the homeless fourth prince of the Winged Clan, he surely has the pride of the nobles.

114
00:08:59,900 --> 00:09:01,400
If he yields to you easily,

115
00:09:01,400 --> 00:09:03,200
that means he'll yield to others easily, too.

116
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:05,900
The homeless fourth prince?

117
00:09:07,400 --> 00:09:10,000
I've spent a lot of effort

118
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:13,800
in making myself the Protectorate General of Ningzhou.

119
00:09:13,800 --> 00:09:16,200
However, even so, most of the Winged Ones

120
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:21,000
still take the Yu Family as their leader.

121
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:24,200
That's why I came here to verify Yi Wuyou's identity.

122
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:27,000
I've confirmed that he's the Fourth Prince, Yu Linkong.

123
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:29,400
Father, in your opinion, should we recruit him

124
00:09:29,400 --> 00:09:31,000
to convince the Winged Ones to join us?

125
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:33,600
Or should we use him as our king to stage a rebellion?

126
00:09:33,600 --> 00:09:35,400
Use him as our king?

127
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:40,600
He's not influential enough right now.

128
00:09:41,800 --> 00:09:43,600
With his current influence,

129
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:45,100
even if he does become our king,

130
00:09:45,100 --> 00:09:48,200
he'll only be your puppet.

131
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:50,500
You do have a point.

132
00:09:50,500 --> 00:09:53,000
However, the Emperor of Chao is powerful.

133
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:54,700
We shouldn't go against him head-to-head.

134
00:09:54,700 --> 00:09:57,400
We should try to persuade the Fourth Prince to join us first.

135
00:09:57,400 --> 00:09:59,000
Since that's the case,

136
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:00,400
Father, you may use the engagement

137
00:10:00,400 --> 00:10:04,000
between the Xue Family and Yu Family as your excuse next time.

138
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:06,000
As long as I get married to Yu Linkong,

139
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:09,800
the Winged Ones will stop putting you on the spot.

140
00:10:09,800 --> 00:10:14,200
If only your brothers were half as smart as you.

141
00:10:14,200 --> 00:10:16,700
If so, I wouldn't need to endure

142
00:10:16,700 --> 00:10:19,400
that young man's arrogant demeanor at such an old age.

143
00:10:23,300 --> 00:10:26,380
By the way, how are you doing in Tianqi?

144
00:10:26,380 --> 00:10:28,300
Are you doing well?

145
00:10:28,300 --> 00:10:32,000
Father, only now you're caring about me?

146
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:34,500
It seems like I'm doing well then.

147
00:10:35,800 --> 00:10:37,100
Father, don't worry.

148
00:10:37,100 --> 00:10:41,000
I will do everything I can to assist you.

149
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:42,300
I shouldn't stay here for too long.

150
00:10:42,300 --> 00:10:43,800
I'll head back now.

151
00:10:43,800 --> 00:10:45,300
Okay.

152
00:10:48,400 --> 00:10:51,200
Why does the palace look so lifeless during the Emperor's Natal Day?

153
00:10:51,200 --> 00:10:53,500
I heard that His Majesty forbade us from holding a birthday banquet.

154
00:10:53,500 --> 00:10:55,200
Is that so?

155
00:11:00,700 --> 00:11:02,400
Stop right there.

156
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:06,000
I almost forgot.

157
00:11:17,400 --> 00:11:21,300
Why is he pulling a long face?

158
00:11:24,000 --> 00:11:26,300
You're already here.

159
00:11:26,300 --> 00:11:28,800
Why are you still sneaking around?

160
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:36,200
Greetings, Your Majesty.

161
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:38,000
How did you know I was here?

162
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:40,200
I knew you were here since you entered the palace.

163
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:44,800
If not, do you think Ling Yun dares to let you enter the palace?

164
00:11:47,900 --> 00:11:49,200
Speak.

165
00:11:49,200 --> 00:11:51,200
What are you doing here?

166
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:53,400
I'm here to make a report about my progress.

167
00:12:04,100 --> 00:12:06,800
Since you came to Guangyang Palace,

168
00:12:06,800 --> 00:12:08,800
I thought you had something important to report to me.

169
00:12:08,800 --> 00:12:12,700
In the end, these are all just trivial matters.

170
00:12:16,400 --> 00:12:20,600
Your Majesty, it's lively outside the palace.

171
00:12:20,600 --> 00:12:24,500
But why does Guangyang Palace look so lifeless?

172
00:12:25,900 --> 00:12:29,000
What has that got to do with me?

173
00:12:30,500 --> 00:12:33,600
All these celebrations belong to other people.

174
00:12:33,600 --> 00:12:35,700
They have nothing to do with me.

175
00:12:36,500 --> 00:12:39,400
These are just temporary moments.

176
00:12:46,000 --> 00:12:48,600
I thought today was your birthday?

177
00:12:50,600 --> 00:12:52,000
I understand now.

178
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:56,100
No one told you since Jie Haitian is no longer around.

179
00:12:56,100 --> 00:12:59,000
In order not to let people predict my destiny,

180
00:12:59,000 --> 00:13:02,200
Jie Haitian hid my star on purpose.

181
00:13:02,800 --> 00:13:07,200
The people outside don't know my true birthday.

182
00:13:07,200 --> 00:13:08,900
They can enjoy the occasion.

183
00:13:08,900 --> 00:13:12,800
But there's no need for me to hold a fake celebration.

184
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:16,400
Your Majesty, I have a suggestion.

185
00:13:17,600 --> 00:13:21,600
You should keep your mind free of any thoughts today.

186
00:13:21,600 --> 00:13:25,400
Forget about the official affairs.

187
00:13:26,200 --> 00:13:29,800
Don't treat yourself as the emperor today.

188
00:13:29,800 --> 00:13:33,400
You should join me on the streets, admire the lanterns, and have fun.

189
00:13:33,400 --> 00:13:35,000
Lanterns?

190
00:13:44,500 --> 00:13:45,600
Excellent!

191
00:13:45,600 --> 00:13:47,300
Again!

192
00:13:47,300 --> 00:13:50,300
Excellent!

193
00:13:53,600 --> 00:13:54,900
Look!

194
00:13:56,500 --> 00:13:58,800
Excellent!

195
00:14:21,200 --> 00:14:23,000
Two guests, please.

196
00:14:42,800 --> 00:14:44,600
I'm sure it's rare for you to witness such scenes.

197
00:14:44,600 --> 00:14:49,200
Before this, I was a young general that was born in the city.

198
00:14:49,200 --> 00:14:51,100
I'm not like the nobles

199
00:14:51,100 --> 00:14:54,200
who are out of touch with reality.

200
00:14:54,200 --> 00:14:56,000
Were you born here?

201
00:14:56,000 --> 00:14:58,600
Seems like you don't know me well enough.

202
00:14:58,600 --> 00:14:59,800
I wasn't born here.

203
00:14:59,800 --> 00:15:02,000
I was born in Weidi.

204
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:04,600
Have you ever heard of the saying

205
00:15:04,600 --> 00:15:09,000
"The Fan Family of Weidi is as noble as the Imperial Family"?

206
00:15:10,200 --> 00:15:14,300
That means the Fan Family is favored by the emperor.

207
00:15:14,300 --> 00:15:16,200
If so, aren't you curious

208
00:15:16,200 --> 00:15:20,400
as to why I'm so lenient toward the Fan Family?

209
00:15:22,800 --> 00:15:27,600
Without Official Fan, you wouldn't be able to be absent from court

210
00:15:27,600 --> 00:15:30,000
and enjoy your own sweet time.

211
00:15:32,110 --> 00:15:35,780
Why did it sound like you were criticizing me just now?

212
00:15:36,600 --> 00:15:38,400
Was I wrong?

213
00:15:39,800 --> 00:15:42,100
You're both right and wrong.

214
00:15:42,100 --> 00:15:46,400
The Fan Family is the only blood relative I have left.

215
00:15:47,500 --> 00:15:49,500
The old madam raised me.

216
00:15:49,500 --> 00:15:53,000
Naturally, I wouldn't be too strict with them.

217
00:15:53,900 --> 00:15:55,800
However, greed has gotten the better of them.

218
00:15:55,800 --> 00:15:57,700
They are now...

219
00:16:01,800 --> 00:16:04,600
- Why am I telling you this?
- They're setting fireworks in front!

220
00:16:04,600 --> 00:16:06,200
Let's check it out!

221
00:16:06,200 --> 00:16:08,200
Okay. Let's go!

222
00:16:18,100 --> 00:16:19,400
Look!

223
00:16:26,600 --> 00:16:28,200
Look!

224
00:16:33,000 --> 00:16:39,100
♫ I had witnessed the bright fireworks several
times flashing in the air ♫

225
00:16:39,100 --> 00:16:45,200
♫ I had witnessed several beautiful sunsets ♫

226
00:16:45,200 --> 00:16:51,200
♫ Eyes filled with warmth when you passed by ♫

227
00:16:51,200 --> 00:16:57,200
♫ Just like a lost amber, waiting for you to pick it up ♫

228
00:16:57,200 --> 00:17:03,300
♫ I was once the lonely moonlight that led a reclusive life ♫

229
00:17:03,300 --> 00:17:09,400
♫ I've not been able to cry for a very long time,
but I'm now shedding tears because of you ♫

230
00:17:09,400 --> 00:17:15,400
♫ Wandering and being lonely for most of my life,
but you came into my life and changed everything ♫

231
00:17:15,400 --> 00:17:21,500
♫ You're my ups and downs ♫

232
00:17:21,500 --> 00:17:27,500
♫ A cold and lonely moonlight that dissipates
with the night breeze ♫

233
00:17:27,500 --> 00:17:33,600
♫ I'm willing to lie in your arms ♫

234
00:17:33,600 --> 00:17:39,800
♫ So, I was gazing at the nearest distance all along ♫

235
00:17:39,800 --> 00:17:42,000
What do you think about the matter just now?

236
00:17:42,800 --> 00:17:45,600
Your Majesty, it's getting late.

237
00:17:45,600 --> 00:17:47,500
I shall take my leave.

238
00:17:49,600 --> 00:17:50,900
You...

239
00:17:56,800 --> 00:17:58,200
You...

240
00:18:01,600 --> 00:18:03,600
You should rest early.

241
00:18:10,400 --> 00:18:13,000
That's the wrong way.

