253
00:19:16,300 --> 00:19:22,900
♫ Pouring everything into your heart ♫

254
00:19:34,600 --> 00:19:37,300
Your Majesty, all protectorate generals

255
00:19:37,300 --> 00:19:40,900
have assumed their positions except for the one in Yuezhou.

256
00:19:40,900 --> 00:19:43,600
Please take a look.

257
00:19:58,200 --> 00:20:02,000
So, do you have any candidates in mind for the Protectorate General of Yuezhou?

258
00:20:02,000 --> 00:20:05,600
I do have a suggestion.

259
00:20:05,600 --> 00:20:07,000
Speak.

260
00:20:07,000 --> 00:20:09,100
Although Yuezhou is a remote area,

261
00:20:09,100 --> 00:20:12,400
if we attack from there, we can conquer Zhongzhou, Wanzhou, and Lanzhou.

262
00:20:12,400 --> 00:20:15,800
If we retreat from there, we can protect ourselves by using the mountain terrains.

263
00:20:15,800 --> 00:20:17,400
Your Majesty, you've already chosen

264
00:20:17,400 --> 00:20:18,700
Ji Fengyan, a member of Mount Beimang's Heluo Clan,

265
00:20:18,700 --> 00:20:20,600
to be the Protectorate General of Wanzhou.

266
00:20:20,600 --> 00:20:24,500
Therefore, we mustn't choose another Heluo to be the Protectorate General of Yuezhou.

267
00:20:24,500 --> 00:20:26,400
As for the suitable candidate,

268
00:20:26,400 --> 00:20:31,400
I think he should be your trusted aide who has served you for many years.

269
00:20:32,200 --> 00:20:35,700
Are you saying that you're recommending yourself

270
00:20:35,700 --> 00:20:38,500
to be the Protectorate General of Yuezhou?

271
00:20:40,800 --> 00:20:43,200
I was just joking around.

272
00:20:43,200 --> 00:20:45,200
Tianqi has plenty of affairs to deal with.

273
00:20:45,200 --> 00:20:48,200
I cannot manage them without you.

274
00:20:48,200 --> 00:20:49,600
Continue.

275
00:20:49,600 --> 00:20:52,900
I have two candidates in mind for the Protectorate General of Yuezhou.

276
00:20:52,900 --> 00:20:55,100
Yu Shining and Zuo Jintian.

277
00:20:55,100 --> 00:20:56,800
Your Majesty, you've already selected

278
00:20:56,800 --> 00:20:59,500
Yu Shining to be the Protectorate General of Lanzhou.

279
00:20:59,500 --> 00:21:01,600
Therefore, I think Zuo Jintian is the most suitable candidate

280
00:21:01,600 --> 00:21:05,200
to be the Protectorate General of Yuezhou.

281
00:21:05,200 --> 00:21:09,300
Now, I guess only Zuo Jintian is the only person

282
00:21:09,300 --> 00:21:12,200
who has the necessary experience and abilities?

283
00:21:12,200 --> 00:21:15,200
Your Majesty is wise indeed.

284
00:21:24,800 --> 00:21:26,400
Father.

285
00:21:31,800 --> 00:21:36,700
Ping'er, I've arranged a date for you and Shengnan today.

286
00:21:36,700 --> 00:21:39,200
Do not forget your manners.

287
00:21:40,200 --> 00:21:42,000
Yes, Father.

288
00:21:45,110 --> 00:21:46,180
Brother Fan!

289
00:21:46,180 --> 00:21:48,090
My brother!

290
00:21:52,630 --> 00:21:53,920
Great Steward!

291
00:21:53,920 --> 00:21:57,900
My brother, you're still calling me that?

292
00:21:57,900 --> 00:22:00,400
Aren't you being too courteous here?

293
00:22:00,400 --> 00:22:02,177
[Zuo Jintian, Xiayang's military commissioner]
I'm a brute.

294
00:22:02,177 --> 00:22:05,705
[Zuo Shengnan, daughter of Zuo Jintian]
Please pardon my manners.

295
00:22:06,740 --> 00:22:08,810
Shengnan.

296
00:22:08,810 --> 00:22:11,720
Greetings, Great Steward.

297
00:22:11,720 --> 00:22:15,420
It's been a few years since we met. You're all grown up.

298
00:22:16,660 --> 00:22:21,130
Ping'er, come here. Greet Uncle Zuo and Shengnan.

299
00:22:26,800 --> 00:22:29,440
Greetings, Official Zuo. Miss Zuo.

300
00:22:29,440 --> 00:22:31,220
Young Master Fan.

301
00:22:32,930 --> 00:22:34,720
What should you call him?

302
00:22:37,320 --> 00:22:39,650
Uncle Zuo.

303
00:22:39,650 --> 00:22:41,200
Excellent!

304
00:22:41,200 --> 00:22:44,250
My brother, I've prepared liquor for you in the courtyard.

305
00:22:44,250 --> 00:22:45,340
Let's head to the courtyard.

306
00:22:45,340 --> 00:22:47,860
Sure.

307
00:22:47,860 --> 00:22:49,660
Please.

308
00:22:50,620 --> 00:22:53,050
My brother, let's catch up with each other.

309
00:22:53,050 --> 00:22:56,310
We shall drink until we drop. Please.

310
00:23:00,800 --> 00:23:03,560
Young Master Fan, there's no need to be this formal.

311
00:23:26,030 --> 00:23:28,080
Brother Jintian, let us drink.

312
00:23:28,080 --> 00:23:29,450
Okay.

313
00:23:32,080 --> 00:23:34,960
From now on, we're a family.

314
00:23:34,960 --> 00:23:38,900
No matter if it's matters inside or outside the court, it'll be no problem.

315
00:23:39,900 --> 00:23:40,720
Come on.

316
00:23:40,720 --> 00:23:46,010
Brother Fan, the position of Yuezhou's protectorate general is still vacant.

317
00:23:46,010 --> 00:23:49,030
Does His Majesty have another candidate in mind?

318
00:23:49,030 --> 00:23:50,470
Before this, His Majesty

319
00:23:50,470 --> 00:23:53,780
wanted to announce the candidate during the Ceremony of Stars.

320
00:23:53,780 --> 00:23:58,400
However, an assassination occurred. That's why he didn't announce it.

321
00:23:58,400 --> 00:24:01,420
Brother Fan, I got to where I am today

322
00:24:01,420 --> 00:24:04,240
by participating in wars and battles.

323
00:24:05,380 --> 00:24:10,000
If Yu Xiuming doesn't show any respect to me,

324
00:24:10,000 --> 00:24:13,550
I have my own army.

325
00:24:13,550 --> 00:24:17,480
I can create my own kingdom.

326
00:24:18,610 --> 00:24:23,040
Brother Jintian, you shouldn't say this in front of outsiders.

327
00:24:23,040 --> 00:24:25,850
Brother Fan, you and I are in-laws.

328
00:24:25,850 --> 00:24:27,640
You're not an outsider.

329
00:24:27,640 --> 00:24:30,240
That's precisely it.

330
00:24:30,240 --> 00:24:34,910
If so, today, I shall tell you a secret.

331
00:24:34,910 --> 00:24:39,100
His Majesty said he would elect you

332
00:24:39,100 --> 00:24:42,900
as the Protectorate General of Yuezhou.

333
00:24:42,900 --> 00:24:46,380
That's why I'm willing to give you this guarantee.

334
00:24:46,380 --> 00:24:47,840
When the wedding is over,

335
00:24:47,840 --> 00:24:51,770
my brother, you can wait in Xiayang for His Majesty's edict.

336
00:24:51,770 --> 00:24:54,320
I hope so. Come on.

337
00:24:54,320 --> 00:24:56,070
Sure.

338
00:25:05,350 --> 00:25:09,800
Excellent!

339
00:25:19,720 --> 00:25:21,350
Congratulations, Commander-in-Chief.

340
00:25:21,350 --> 00:25:23,220
No, I should address you as Marquis Zuo now.

341
00:25:23,220 --> 00:25:25,310
Everyone, to Marquis Zuo!

342
00:25:25,310 --> 00:25:26,350
Here.

343
00:25:26,350 --> 00:25:28,700
- To Marquis Zuo.
- Congratulations, Marquis Zuo.

344
00:25:28,700 --> 00:25:30,780
Congratulations, Marquis Zuo.

345
00:25:33,270 --> 00:25:35,730
Have a seat.

346
00:25:35,730 --> 00:25:39,410
Actually, the title of marquis is insignificant.

347
00:25:39,410 --> 00:25:43,770
Xie Yu'an also received the title of marquis. Right?

348
00:25:43,770 --> 00:25:48,030
However, being the Protectorate General of the nine states

349
00:25:48,030 --> 00:25:50,290
and commanding the army of the state,

350
00:25:50,290 --> 00:25:56,240
that's how you know His Majesty acknowledges you.

351
00:25:56,240 --> 00:25:59,240
Yuezhou is just in the south of Xiayang.

352
00:25:59,240 --> 00:26:03,620
You were already chosen as Yuezhou's protectorate general long ago.

353
00:26:03,620 --> 00:26:05,720
That's right. Marquis, he's right.

354
00:26:05,720 --> 00:26:08,120
Uncle Zuo, my father had told you time and time again

355
00:26:08,120 --> 00:26:10,680
that you shouldn't reveal this news to outsiders before the edict is out.

356
00:26:10,680 --> 00:26:12,590
There are no outsiders here.

357
00:26:12,590 --> 00:26:13,850
We're a family.

358
00:26:13,850 --> 00:26:17,260
That's right. We're a family.

359
00:26:17,260 --> 00:26:21,990
Now, the eldest son of the Fan Family will be marrying your daughter.

360
00:26:21,990 --> 00:26:26,980
Marquis, you will lead a carefree and easy life under Great Steward's care.

361
00:26:26,980 --> 00:26:30,030
Here. To our marquis.

362
00:26:30,030 --> 00:26:32,980
To his son-in-law.

363
00:26:32,980 --> 00:26:34,920
Come on.

364
00:26:34,920 --> 00:26:37,370
To our marquis.

365
00:26:52,750 --> 00:26:56,350
I overheard the conversation between you all just now.

366
00:26:56,350 --> 00:26:58,700
Congratulations, Young Master.

367
00:27:35,560 --> 00:27:37,130
Here.

368
00:27:38,580 --> 00:27:42,200
Guys, we'll reach Xiayang soon.

369
00:27:42,200 --> 00:27:46,870
Once we reach Xiayang, we will rest for a couple of days and have our fill!

370
00:27:46,870 --> 00:27:49,430
Come on! Let's give it one last push!

371
00:27:49,430 --> 00:27:50,530
- Come on!
- Come on.

372
00:27:50,530 --> 00:27:54,110
One, two, three, push!

373
00:28:03,870 --> 00:28:08,560
Seems like His Majesty is going to elect the Protectorate General of Yuezhou.

374
00:28:08,560 --> 00:28:11,030
Official Zuo will definitely get the position.

375
00:28:11,030 --> 00:28:13,130
Precisely.

376
00:28:15,080 --> 00:28:19,970
Yuezhou? Isn't that the place Sister Lian is migrating to?

377
00:28:19,970 --> 00:28:22,410
Official Bai. You may enter.

378
00:28:22,410 --> 00:28:24,200
Yes.

379
00:28:39,080 --> 00:28:41,700
Greetings, Your Majesty.

380
00:28:41,700 --> 00:28:44,230
These are the records from observing the stars.

381
00:28:51,560 --> 00:28:53,490
Leave it here.

382
00:28:59,030 --> 00:29:01,230
Your Majesty is in a bad mood.

383
00:29:03,960 --> 00:29:07,020
How did you know?

384
00:29:09,480 --> 00:29:14,040
Your Majesty, you will carve things whenever you're in a good or bad mood.

385
00:29:14,040 --> 00:29:16,510
But the difference is,

386
00:29:17,290 --> 00:29:20,870
your carvings look terrible when you're in a bad mood.

387
00:29:30,220 --> 00:29:32,700
Do you know what this is?

388
00:29:32,700 --> 00:29:33,840
What is it?

389
00:29:33,840 --> 00:29:37,510
It's called a wolf in sheep's clothing.

390
00:29:40,030 --> 00:29:45,550
There are plenty of people like this in the imperial court.

391
00:29:47,010 --> 00:29:49,960
Sounds deep to me.

392
00:29:49,960 --> 00:29:54,620
You can learn how to disguise yourself, too.

393
00:29:54,620 --> 00:29:56,450
Just pretend to be weak.

394
00:29:56,450 --> 00:29:59,870
Sometimes it's pretty useful.

395
00:30:00,630 --> 00:30:02,700
I won't learn that.

396
00:30:02,700 --> 00:30:06,530
Your Majesty, I think you've seen through Great Steward Fan's plot long ago.

397
00:30:12,720 --> 00:30:15,030
You're pretty clear about the situation.

398
00:30:15,890 --> 00:30:18,150
Your Majesty, since you have doubts,

399
00:30:18,150 --> 00:30:23,620
why are you still electing Zuo Jintian as the Protectorate General of Yuezhou?

400
00:30:25,150 --> 00:30:27,130
Zuo Jintian is not my cause of concern.

401
00:30:27,130 --> 00:30:30,150
However, the marriage alliance between them is pretty tricky.

402
00:30:30,150 --> 00:30:33,270
So, in your opinion, what should I do?

403
00:30:34,010 --> 00:30:38,100
Since they're partners in crime, they depend on each other.

404
00:30:38,100 --> 00:30:42,460
If one of them loses its edge, the other won't be able to achieve anything.

405
00:30:42,460 --> 00:30:47,080
I suddenly have a great idea.

406
00:30:59,370 --> 00:31:02,430
Seems like another official is going to be sacrificed.

407
00:31:03,200 --> 00:31:04,670
Not bad at all.

408
00:31:04,670 --> 00:31:07,830
You can become my bosom friend.

409
00:31:07,830 --> 00:31:11,880
Please don't say that. Your bosom friends usually end up miserable.

410
00:31:14,720 --> 00:31:18,700
If there's nothing else, I shall take my leave.

411
00:31:18,700 --> 00:31:20,300
Wait.

412
00:31:30,980 --> 00:31:34,000
From today onward, you shall be the supervisor of the Bureau of Astrology.

413
00:31:34,000 --> 00:31:35,450
It's your reward.

414
00:31:35,450 --> 00:31:37,540
Thank you, Your Majesty.

415
00:31:41,600 --> 00:31:43,900
She doesn't have any propriety at all.

416
00:31:53,170 --> 00:31:56,930
Since they're partners in crime, they depend on each other.

417
00:31:56,930 --> 00:31:58,550
If one of them loses their edge,

418
00:31:58,550 --> 00:32:00,810
the other won't be able to achieve anything.

419
00:32:00,810 --> 00:32:03,420
The Great Steward is in charge of official affairs.

420
00:32:03,420 --> 00:32:06,970
And now, he wants an in-law who's in charge of the military?

421
00:32:08,200 --> 00:32:12,100
Zuo Jintian, you can forget about being

422
00:32:12,100 --> 00:32:14,450
the Protectorate General of Yuezhou.

423
00:32:33,800 --> 00:32:35,310
Ling Yun.

424
00:32:38,290 --> 00:32:40,580
Send this to Xiayang immediately.

425
00:32:40,580 --> 00:32:42,090
Yes, Your Majesty.

426
00:32:47,220 --> 00:32:49,800
[Fan Residence]

427
00:32:53,760 --> 00:32:57,710
Sir, His Majesty has selected Zhu Ying as the Protectorate General of Yuezhou.

428
00:32:58,140 --> 00:32:59,810
How is that possible?

429
00:33:00,520 --> 00:33:02,260
What is His Majesty thinking?

430
00:33:02,260 --> 00:33:04,980
He said he would elect Zuo Jintian last time.

431
00:33:06,260 --> 00:33:08,340
How could he trick me like this?

432
00:33:08,340 --> 00:33:10,450
Where's the edict? Give it to me! I'll seek an audience with him!

433
00:33:10,450 --> 00:33:11,580
It's too late.

434
00:33:11,580 --> 00:33:14,510
Commander Ling has ordered his man to deliver it to Xiayang in haste.

435
00:33:14,510 --> 00:33:16,690
He wants Zuo Jintian, the Military Commissioner of Xiayang,

436
00:33:16,690 --> 00:33:17,960
to impart the edict to Zhu Ying.

437
00:33:17,960 --> 00:33:20,840
Sir, please think of something.

438
00:33:23,920 --> 00:33:26,660
What exactly is he up to?

439
00:33:26,660 --> 00:33:30,020
We can figure out His Majesty's intention later.

440
00:33:30,020 --> 00:33:33,090
We should try to calm Zuo Jintian down.

441
00:33:33,090 --> 00:33:36,070
This is the key to winning Zuo Jintian to our side.

442
00:33:36,070 --> 00:33:38,740
I mustn't let him vent his anger on me.

443
00:33:38,740 --> 00:33:41,170
Sir, you mean...

444
00:33:42,720 --> 00:33:45,970
His Majesty recalled Bai Lu from the ceremony.

445
00:33:45,970 --> 00:33:50,160
And he spared Qihai Lian and the others because of her.

446
00:33:50,160 --> 00:33:54,760
Who knows if he has changed his mind because of her?

447
00:33:54,760 --> 00:33:57,880
His Majesty knew that Zhu Ying was infatuated with Qihai Lian.

448
00:33:57,880 --> 00:34:01,310
He has been lenient toward Qihai Lian since the beginning.

449
00:34:01,310 --> 00:34:04,900
Even so, he sends Zhu Ying to escort the people of Yebei during their migration as punishment.

450
00:34:04,900 --> 00:34:07,720
And now, he's electing him as the Protectorate General of Yuezhou?

451
00:34:07,720 --> 00:34:12,690
It's obvious that he wants the people of Yebei to migrate to Yuezhou smoothly.

452
00:34:12,690 --> 00:34:16,850
Seems like Bai Lu has contributed much to this plan.

453
00:34:16,850 --> 00:34:22,110
Send a letter to Zuo Jintian and tell him to calm down

454
00:34:22,110 --> 00:34:24,300
and that everything is negotiable

455
00:34:24,300 --> 00:34:27,330
as long as Bai Lu is gone.

456
00:34:27,330 --> 00:34:29,110
Yes, sir.

457
00:34:33,320 --> 00:34:37,140
My Lady, these are the gifts meant for the Cai Family.

458
00:34:39,290 --> 00:34:41,510
Father-in-law always treated the Cai Family with leniency.

459
00:34:41,510 --> 00:34:44,370
We should prepare more gifts for the Cai Family.

460
00:34:44,370 --> 00:34:45,890
Yes.

461
00:34:51,120 --> 00:34:52,880
Young Master.

462
00:34:58,040 --> 00:35:00,250
You guys may leave.

463
00:35:00,250 --> 00:35:02,800
Yes, Madam.

464
00:35:15,320 --> 00:35:17,320
Dear, you're back.

465
00:35:18,140 --> 00:35:21,280
I've prepared tea for you. Here.

466
00:35:21,280 --> 00:35:23,140
That's unnecessary.

467
00:35:27,120 --> 00:35:29,130
Dear, you came back early today.

468
00:35:29,130 --> 00:35:31,060
Are you having dinner at home?

469
00:35:31,060 --> 00:35:32,960
Do you feel like having anything?

470
00:35:32,960 --> 00:35:35,430
I'll tell the kitchen to prepare them.

471
00:35:35,430 --> 00:35:38,070
Last time, you said the sea cucumber soup was nice.

472
00:35:38,070 --> 00:35:39,790
I will make arrangements for it.

473
00:35:39,790 --> 00:35:42,710
Father wants you to write a letter to Zuo...

474
00:35:44,520 --> 00:35:46,760
He wants you to write to Father-in-law.

475
00:35:50,180 --> 00:35:53,560
Is there something Father-in-law cannot tell him personally?

476
00:35:54,810 --> 00:35:57,980
Father said His Majesty have selected

477
00:35:57,980 --> 00:36:00,560
Zhu Ying as the Protectorate General of Yuezhou.

478
00:36:02,930 --> 00:36:06,470
My father thought that he would be the Protectorate General of Yuezhou for sure.

479
00:36:06,470 --> 00:36:09,420
Since that's not the case, he will surely be enraged.

480
00:36:09,420 --> 00:36:13,960
Is Father-in-law worried that my father might do something unthinkable out of anger?

481
00:36:14,940 --> 00:36:17,190
I will write to him immediately.

482
00:36:33,900 --> 00:36:38,280
Father wants him to calm down and to not speak too much.

483
00:36:38,280 --> 00:36:40,290
He will find other opportunities.

484
00:36:40,290 --> 00:36:42,310
He wants Father-in-law to calm down.

485
00:36:42,310 --> 00:36:44,430
There are still plenty of chances.

486
00:36:46,770 --> 00:36:48,720
Chances?

487
00:36:49,630 --> 00:36:55,730
So, is Father-in-law saying that this isn't His Majesty's intention?

488
00:36:58,080 --> 00:37:00,830
You and Father are alike indeed.

489
00:37:07,390 --> 00:37:10,980
Dear, please explain what Father-in-law meant.

490
00:37:10,980 --> 00:37:13,090
My father is a straight man.

491
00:37:13,090 --> 00:37:17,060
He might not be convinced by such blurry reasons.

492
00:37:20,770 --> 00:37:25,630
My father said His Majesty has been showing favoritism toward Director Bai of the Bureau of Astrology.

493
00:37:25,630 --> 00:37:28,960
This should be related to her.

494
00:37:29,400 --> 00:37:31,740
Father is thinking of a way to get rid of her.

495
00:37:31,740 --> 00:37:36,820
Everything is negotiable as long as she's not by His Majesty's side.

496
00:37:38,390 --> 00:37:41,010
All right, I got it.

497
00:38:05,420 --> 00:38:07,240
Fang Hen.

498
00:38:16,420 --> 00:38:19,390
- My Lady.
- Deliver 500 silver dimes to Lieutenant Tan.

499
00:38:19,390 --> 00:38:22,780
Tell him that Mother is suffering a relapse and that she needs these herbs urgently.

500
00:38:22,780 --> 00:38:25,930
Tell him that he must deliver them by tonight at all costs.

501
00:38:25,930 --> 00:38:27,620
Yes.

502
00:38:34,960 --> 00:38:38,020
The tea is cold. Let me change it for you.

503
00:38:38,020 --> 00:38:40,420
It's your favorite Tianyaxue.

504
00:38:41,110 --> 00:38:43,420
Tianyaxue is a tea we consume during summer.

505
00:38:43,420 --> 00:38:46,640
You don't need to entertain me. I'm busy.

506
00:38:54,560 --> 00:38:57,630
All right. I understand.

507
00:39:02,110 --> 00:39:04,180
Dear, take care.

508
00:39:10,000 --> 00:39:12,900
There's no need to figure out my preferences.

509
00:39:12,900 --> 00:39:17,150
There's no need to keep all these trinkets here in the house either.

510
00:39:17,870 --> 00:39:22,020
These things are not for pleasing people.

511
00:39:22,020 --> 00:39:24,280
You don't need to force yourself.

512
00:39:44,300 --> 00:39:46,580
