516
00:40:16,680 --> 00:40:19,110
But now, they're still 20 li away?

517
00:40:19,110 --> 00:40:21,870
Are they crawling here?

518
00:40:21,870 --> 00:40:24,770
That brat is still wet behind the ears.

519
00:40:24,770 --> 00:40:27,320
How dare he get ahead of himself.

520
00:40:27,320 --> 00:40:30,550
He was still sucking on his mother's breast

521
00:40:30,550 --> 00:40:33,420
when I was fighting in wars!

522
00:40:35,080 --> 00:40:38,860
You want to steal my position from me?

523
00:40:39,960 --> 00:40:43,010
Relay my order! Gather 30,000 elite troops at once!

524
