528
00:40:58,770 --> 00:41:02,010
It was at that moment that His Majesty said

529
00:41:02,010 --> 00:41:04,630
he would build a canal that would provide easy access

530
00:41:04,630 --> 00:41:07,130
from all directions when the world is at peace.

