534
00:41:18,400 --> 00:41:21,010
I'm the only one who managed to escape!

535
00:41:21,700 --> 00:41:23,490
Get up first.

536
00:41:23,980 --> 00:41:26,430
Calm down. Take your time.

537
00:41:26,430 --> 00:41:27,750
Tell me what's going on.

538
00:41:27,750 --> 00:41:29,420
I don't know!

539
00:41:29,420 --> 00:41:34,120
Marquis Zuo said he would kill all of your men!

540
00:41:35,010 --> 00:41:37,230
